data.description: Don't miss this opportunity to own this 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom home in Heritage Valley Subdivision. The home features lots of new updates including hardwood flooring, carpet, deck and newer stainless steel appliances. There are 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms including a large main bedroom en suite. Main level features a large living room with a fireplace, 1 bedroom, kitchen, dining room and 3/4 bath. The lower level has a large gathering room with a fireplace, 3 bedrooms, full bath and a finished laundry room. The home is centrally located and close to everything Valparaiso has to offer. This is an Estate Sale and being Sold As Is. Schedule your showing today.
